  "body": "Add a flag like \"--Init.ForceBlockProduction\" which would default to false but when set to true will try to produce block on every slot. This should be hidden from docs and only used for testing and verifying if we can produce block quickly even if we are not validator or not selected for block production (which is often a case on mainnet for very long time).\r\n\r\nAlso it will try to use local txPool and produce blocks based on it all the time so we can quickly check if we have any issue with stateDb (if corrupted).",
